LanguageData.Rimgate_GoauldTeltak.label: Goa'uld Tel'tak
LanguageData.Rimgate_GoauldTeltak.description: Goa'uld Tel'taks are small transportships capable of carrying people, items, or animals. Can be used for sending gifts, transporting people or supplies, surprise attacks, or reinforcing battles.
